{"word":"ἀστοχέω","slug":"ἀστοχέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀστοχέω</el></b> [<el>ἀ-</el><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ priv.\">priv.</a>, <el>στόχος</el> ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> serving as a mark for a missile’] <b><i>miss,</i></b> of failure in endeavor or objective<b>:</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀστοχέω\">ἀστοχέω</a></el> <i>miss the target</i> (of truth) <b><a href='B:620 2:18'>2 Ti 2:18</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πίστις\">πίστις</a></el> <b>6:21; <i>deviate,</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:610 1:6'>1 Ti 1:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄστοργος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀστραπή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}